snippet.title: Metro x PUBG MOBILE
snippet.description:
You may have claimed a Chicken Dinner... but you haven't seen anything yet! 🗺️ 

Be sure to stay tuned for our collaboration with Metro Exodus, the latest video game in the acclaimed Metro series! More details coming soon! 👉 https://pubgmobile.live/Metro
